First restaurant that I’ve been to since lockdown and it was great. The staff was friendly and so helpful. Food was fantastic and the wine list was great. Awesome experience, first time tonight. The atmosphere was very relaxing and comfortable and the service was excellent...will be retuning again.

Stopped in for some wine & a bite to eat & absolutely loved this place!  Highly recommend for anyone wanting to enjoy an afternoon sip with some company!  Try some new wine & enjoy the cranberry goat cheese!
Love this place!

This is one of my favorite places in Old Town Lewisville. They have yummy sandwiches, flat-breads, and cheeses. The place is charming and laid back. Great place to relax with friends over a meal and conversation.
The wine is spectacular paired with their cheeseboards or flatbreads, would highly recommend
Great service and people, amazing atmosphere
I simply loved their dishes. I always get good customer service here. The place is well organised and the workers are always very friendly. Would recommend to others.
Friendly staff, great wine, and wonderful food! Try the grilled cheese and soup (lemon one).
Sophisticated, homey, inviting and delicious all in one. Not to mention 1/2 off wine bottles on Wednesdays... love it.
Improving wine menu, and delicious flatbreads. Great atmosphere.
Always a great place to unwind for lunch. Friendly staff, good wine, good food, and nice atmosphere.

this a wonderful place to have lunch or just to have a nice of wine .

Great experience every time. After going a few times and enjoying this wine bar we began to coordinate a group of us who meet almost weekly for wine Wednesday and tanner has given us exceptional service each time!
Staff is friendly. Food is scrumptious and great atmosphere! Very clean and inviting!
Cozy environment,  friendly and attentive service, excellent food and a variety choice of fine wine. Has a bar also. Will definitely frequent this place more often.

Great wine selection & light meal options. Friendly place "where everybody knows your name".

Fantastic

Very relaxing & cozy atmosphere, perfect for a wine bar. Outstanding service, food choices from great appetizers to full meal, great wine selection, and occasional live entertainment. Glad I know about this gem! Old town Lewisville has really been revitalized!

Delicious food and amazing vibes. Great atmosphere. Perfect little gem right in the middle of downtown Lewisville.

Absolutely great experience tonight. Ambiance, wine selection, food, and service were all excellent.The Cheese Board was very tasty. Support a local business and enjoy a great evening in Old Town Lewisville!

Great wine and food. Close to home.
